The owning library of this VI is missing

If a project library owns a VI, the VI cannot be executed or edited unless that project library is loaded into memory. LabVIEW cannot load the project library that owns this VI.

To correct this error, find and load the project library or select File»Disconnect from Library on the VI. Using the Disconnect from Library option breaks the ownership of the VI by the project library. If the project library is password protected, you must provide that password to disconnect the VI from the project library.
